<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2011/09/02/dear-iceland/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Dear Iceland">Dear Iceland</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p>Dear Iceland,</p>
<p>I really want to visit your country in early to mid October. A festival in Sweden has invited me to speak around October 14-16, and would like to make a stopover before or after or both. I am greatly intrigued by Iceland&#8217;s Modern Media Initiative*. Might there be some way I could speak at a university there, or at least meet Icelanders involved with media reform and free speech issues?</p>
<p>Love,</p>
<p>&#8211;Nina</p>
<p>*P.S. OK, not just the Modern Media Initiative. I&#8217;m also intrigued by your giant thermal pools.</p>
</p>
